# Environment Variables

## Development
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/imobix?schema=public
DIRECT_URL=postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/imobix?schema=public

## Production (Render + Supabase)
# DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres.YOUR_PROJECT_REF:YOUR_PASSWORD@aws-1-us-east-2.pooler.supabase.com:6543/postgres?pgbouncer=true
# DIRECT_URL=postgresql://postgres:YOUR_PASSWORD@db.YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co:5432/postgres

## Server
PORT=3000

## Security
BCRYPT_SALT_ROUNDS=10
JWT_SECRET=super-secret-key-change-in-production
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=1d
JWT_REFRESH_SECRET=super-secret-refresh-key-change-in-production
JWT_REFRESH_EXPIRES_IN=7d

## Cloudinary (File Storage)
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your-cloud-name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your-api-key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your-api-secret

## Important Notes:
# 1. DATABASE_URL uses connection pooler (port 6543) with pgbouncer=true
# 2. DIRECT_URL uses direct connection (port 5432) for migrations
# 3. Get your Supabase credentials from: https://app.supabase.com/project/_/settings/database
# 4. Never commit the actual .env file to git
